{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"1212-niambie-sasa-rangi","title":"Niambie … sasa! – Rangi","description":"Tunawauliza mama na baba sababu ya vitu kuwa na rangi tofauti.","language":"Kiswahili","langCode":"sw","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Mutugi Kamundi"],"illustrators":["Rijuta Ghate"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"African Storybook Initiative","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/1212-niambie-sasa-rangi"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/700102/size3/610c0cae5d16405f1f342e373837d71f.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/700102/size6/610c0cae5d16405f1f342e373837d71f.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/5965/size6/14a3b7727bfd63a6e9115a8666f19ea9.jpg","text":"Kwa nini mbingu ni za rangi ya samawati?","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/5966/size6/35fcb11dae640fc4d5f937502de8d248.jpg","text":"Je, ni samawati kila wakati?","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/5967/size6/5f973266e8efbc0f004be351f6e95169.jpg","text":"Kwa nini majani ni ya kijani kibichi?","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/5968/size6/88087a47c4bd04f6840b76b723672ed3.jpg","text":"Sio ya kijani kibichi kila wakati.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/5969/size6/7cc90455b0e43e4e9647d58afda48aa8.jpg","text":"Kwa nini ndizi ni za njano?","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/5970/size6/d1